{"id": "1185896024716353576", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185814596448165981", "author_name": "c10h16o_1001", "author_bot": false, "content": "啊请问游戏里的年代设定是什么时候啊，未来？近未来？维多利亚时代？架空的话有出现过具体年份吗", "timestamp": "2023-12-17T10:47:25.175000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1185897866733027418", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "考慮到是克蘇魯題材，感覺年代大概是洛夫克拉夫特那個年代吧，也就是19世紀末到20世紀初", "timestamp": "2023-12-17T10:54:44.346000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1185900661993381938", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "劇情內拉蒙娜有拿出形狀近似現代的手電筒來，我查了一下，網路上說1902年才有第一隻圓筒形的手電筒誕生出來（但那個時候的手電筒亮的時間很短），所以如果非要對應現實不可的話，應該在1902之後了", "timestamp": "2023-12-17T11:05:50.788000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1185901190538612756", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "926498195226370048", "author_name": "bailin1211", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過，更具體一點是劇情裡有學生拿著相機，而且是相對方便攜帶的，這種誕生的時間點就更晚了，第一台便攜式照相機出現在人們面前是1925年（）", "timestamp": "2023-12-17T11:07:56.803000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
